  "base_path": "/domestic-renewable-heat-incentive",
  "content_id": "21808c37-eb05-49f5-8dca-95201f31929f",
  "description": "Help with renewable energy costs for homeowners and landlords through the RHI scheme.",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>This scheme is closed to new applicants.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You could get money towards renewable heating costs in your home.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"types-of-heating\">Types of heating</h2>\n\n<p>You can claim for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>biomass boilers</li>\n  <li>solar water heating</li>\n  <li>certain heat pumps</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Payments are made for 7 years and are based on the amount of renewable heat made by your heating system.</p>\n\n<p>The money is paid through the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.ofgem.gov.uk/environmental-programmes/domestic-renewable-heat-incentive\">Domestic <abbr title=\"Renewable Heat Incentive\">RHI</abbr> scheme</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"eligibility\">Eligibility</h2>\n\n<p>You can apply if you live in England, Scotland or Wales. You must either:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>own your home</li>\n  <li>be a private or social landlord</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>New build properties will not normally be eligible. The only exception is if you’re building your own home.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"if-you-need-help\">If you need help</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Simple Energy Advice<br>\nTelephone: 0800 444 202<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 8pm  <br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Home Energy Scotland<br>\nTelephone: 0808 808 2282<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 8pm<br>\nSaturday, 9am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a <a href=\"/non-domestic-renewable-heat-incentive\">separate RHI scheme</a> for businesses, the public sector and non-profit organisations.</p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
